data.text:
select sum(oi.quantity) as t, sum(oi.price * oi.quantity), pvo.name, pvo2.name
from sb_order as o
join sb_order_item as oi on o.id = oi.order_id
join sb_product_sku_value as psv on psv.product_id = oi.product_id and psv.sku_id = oi.product_sku_id
join sb_product_sku_value as psv2 on psv2.product_id = oi.product_id and psv2.sku_id = oi.product_sku_id
join sb_product_variant_option as pvo on psv.variant_option_id = pvo.id
join sb_product_variant_option as pvo2 on psv2.variant_option_id = pvo2.id
where o.created_at > '2022-01-14'
and psv.variant_id = 7
and psv2.variant_id = 5
and o.payment_status = 'PAID'
group by psv.variant_option_id, psv2.variant_option_id
order by t desc
